-	Up to 1400sqm Turn Key Office 
-	High quality fit out in place 
-	Massive break out areas and decks 
-	Competitive effective rental on offer 

Situated in the heart of the Portside Hamilton precinct is the opportunity to secure up to 1400sqm of fully fitted out A Grade office. The available space has been designed for the latest social distancing trends and office design practices. Set across a single floor plate, the tenancy has been fitted out with multiple offices, boardroom, meeting rooms/collaboration areas, reception and workstations set up generously for 98 staff. The space offers floor to ceiling windows allowing for an abundance of natural light and has an exclusive deck/balcony space with drinks fridges, BBQs and pool tables. 

The property has a plethora of retail amenity at your doorstep including restaurants, cafes, supermarket and bars. Racecourse road is just a stones throw away and the CBD is easily accessible. The property offers great onsite car parking + ample visitor bays. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.

CBRE and Cushman & Wakefield are proud to present 9 Hercules Street for lease within the heart of the new, thriving Hamilton Portside precinct. 
 
This property provides a fantastic opportunity to secure fully furnished, character office space in an ideal location, just 5km from the Brisbane CBD and 10 minutes from Brisbane Airport. Surrounded by Hamilton’s best cafes and restaurants, and transport nodes such as the bus or city cat, this property is very well positioned for staff amenity. 

Key Features: 

- 300 - 900sqm of fitted space
- Upcoming fit out refurbishment  
- 22 secure parking bays 
- Mix of open plan and offices
- Corporate style reception
- Building signage opportunities
- Character red brick features
- Great exposure fronting KSD
- Onsite café
- Street parking available also 
 
For more information, or to arrange an inspection, please contact the Exclusive Agents.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FULLY FITTED & READY TO OCCUPY CHARACTER OFFICE SPACE!
